    @Alpha
public class GobblinHelixTaskStateTracker
extends AbstractTaskStateTracker
    A concrete extension to AbstractTaskStateTracker for a Gobblin Cluster.

    This class is currently still primitive and will be enhanced once we add more monitoring in place.
